  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Summon The DUDES!</strong> is a quirky 2D puzzle platformer where your most powerful tool is… the <strong>DUDES!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the ability to <strong>Summon The DUDES</strong> to solve puzzles and overcome obstacles, you’ll need to think strategically and use summoning of <strong>DUDES</strong> to clear each level!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148080/extras/f700118d61e46d23ce558dcaeabb2fdd.poster.avif?t=1762308127\" width=640 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148080/extras/f700118d61e46d23ce558dcaeabb2fdd.webm?t=1762308127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148080/extras/f700118d61e46d23ce558dcaeabb2fdd.mp4?t=1762308127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different levels with its own set of puzzles and platforming challenges!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump, run, fall and create the environment you need to pass the levels, using your <strong>The DUDES!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Balance of puzzle-solving and platforming action!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Summon The DUDES!</strong></p></li></ul>",
